New Chapter

No Strings On Me - Chapter 11: Changes (on Wattpad) https://my.w.tt/Jjkgx9NI5V His orders were simple. Bring in the little girl with the big brown eyes. But looking into those eyes Bucky couldn’t do it. Instead he decided to take the little girl named Renee and go on the run with her. No more Strings would hold any of them back. They were both free to have a life. But life isn’t always normal. Sometimes life is just crazy.

title: Spider-Man - Hunt For The Amulet
body:
Tony sends Peter on a mission to Rio De Janeiro to find and recruit a girl named Ava Ayala. But when he gets there, a lot of trouble happens when a power-hungry hunter is after her as well. Follows the MCU Timeline. Takes place a month after The Clash of The Avengers.

New Mission

(Peter’s POV)“Ned…Ned, you there buddy?"I say lightly patting my friend on the cheek."I had a crazy dream,” he groaned,“ We were at your house and Tony Stark was there.” He must’ve been so shocked…

Read more…

title: My boyfriends Endgame Headcanon
body:
My boyfriend has this Endgame headcanon which he told me about a few times during the last year and it would be totally amazing to see it on screen: for the last epic battle against Thanos, the Avengers will need not only the help of the remaining living friends and foes, but also of the dead: So all the fallen hereos will return from Valhalla or whatever After-Place they are, Odin will lead the Einherjer while riding on Sleipnir, Loki will ride on Fenris and lead a frost giant army, the Warrios 3 will be there, Yondu will lead the fallen Ravagers and so on…

We both know that won´t happenend , but I will still be disappointed that I will never see this on screen…
